cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.HC 

This paper deals with the problem of image similarity and the comparison of human and machine perception. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision). The paper also discusses the use of deep convolutional neural networks, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper includes human experiments, which could place it in the category of cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction). Finally, the dataset used in the paper contains images from the wild, which could also make it relevant to cs.MM (Multimedia).
